@startuml seq-19-my-likes
' 序列图19：获取我的点赞列表
title 获取我的点赞列表序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "likes.js" as Front
participant "LikeController" as Ctrl
participant "LikeService" as Svc
participant "LikeMapper.xml" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> Front: 打开"我的点赞"页,切换tab(作品/课程/帖子)
Front -> Ctrl: GET /api/like/my/{userId}
Ctrl -> Svc: myLikes(userId)
Svc -> Mapper: selectMyLikesEnriched(userId)
Mapper -> DB: SELECT lr.*, a.title, a.cover_image, uw.title, c.title, p.title FROM like_record lr LEFT JOIN article a ON ... LEFT JOIN user_work uw ON ... LEFT JOIN course c ON ... LEFT JOIN post p ON ... WHERE lr.user_id=?
DB --> Mapper: List<Map>
Mapper --> Svc: List<LikeVO>
Svc --> Ctrl: List<LikeVO>
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200, data:List}
Front -> Front: _fixUrl()拼接封面图
Front -> Front: 按target_type分组渲染
Front --> User: 显示点赞列表

@enduml
